         MACRO
&L       $VPUT &ID,&DATA
.*
.*       THIS MACRO WORKS WITH THE VPUTSUB MACRO TO REPLACE
.*       OR UPDATE AN ISPF VARIABLE IN THE ISPF VARIABLE POOL
.*
*
*   CALL ISPF AND UPDATE VARIABLE &ID WITH DATA FROM LABEL &DATA
*
         LCLA  &LEN,&LEND
&LEN     SETA  K'&ID
&LEND    SETA  L'&DATA
&L       MVC   @ID(&LEN),=C'&ID'
         MVC   @SPFVAR(&LEND),&DATA
         LH    R14,=H'&LEND'
         ST    R14,@LEN
         BAL   R14,VPUTSUB
         MEND
